541633d543b8d0","tid":1722722,"uid":56813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:27.000Z","msg":"琴晚10:07哨group已經傳咗出嚟<br />\n1048物資站先收到風。。。跟手就即刻封門<br />\n問邊個確認到係物資站個個都話唔知<br />\n我覺得物資站做嘢係好辛苦 但一定要有個人長期mon哨grp通風"},{"pid":"9761d35b82397d5d750e7eb4c7c04c7d68d0cdd8","tid":1722722,"uid":313373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"下... 埋土channel有報有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"087b40586f91565a1429d2296a1fc2807d1cb0e6","tid":1722722,"uid":56813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9761d35b82397d5d750e7eb4c7c04c7d68d0cdd8","tid":1722722,"uid":313373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"下... 埋土channel有報有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"入面個撚個都唔睇grp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06296e22c63959775511ca432c0b60c08348a41f","tid":1722722,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:46:36.000Z","msg":"情報係3女1男 女係紅髮米7高<br />\n咁你搜其他人做乜<br />\n又有咩權搜人身 又冇禮貌<br />\n入黎已經搜左次 入到黎仲要睇你地係度扮大台"},{"pid":"feab461d5bb30f8a870db134e2f84ee8c29048de","tid":1722722,"uid":313373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"087b40586f91565a1429d2296a1fc2807d1cb0e6","tid":1722722,"uid":56813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9761d35b82397d5d750e7eb4c7c04c7d68d0cdd8","tid":1722722,"uid":313373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:40:48.000Z","msg":"下... 埋土channel有報有鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有埋相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T03:41:28.000Z","msg":"入